+# Phase Research: ph.2-core-engine
+
+> Implementation path investigation for the pure game core phase.
+> Phase: ph.2-core-engine | Milestone: M1-core-playable | Mode: mvp
+> Goal: Implement and unit-test the pure game rules in `src/core/` — a functional
+> reducer plus move/push, win check, and an entry-based undo stack. Zero DOM imports.
+> `npm test` runs ≥ 12 unit tests covering move, push, win, undo, history, all passing.
+
+Confidence labels: **HIGH** = verified against the locked context, existing `src/types.ts`,
+`tsconfig.json`, `vitest.config.ts`, and the parent research in this session;
+**MEDIUM** = well-established pattern with one residual interpretation gap;
+**LOW** = speculative or depends on a downstream phase.
+
+---
+
+## Research Scope
+
+Investigate the concrete implementation paths for the pure game core, building on the locked
+decisions D1–D10 in `context.md` and the parent research in
+`bp/research/architecture.md` (State Model, Undo Stack Representation, Win-check Algorithm)
