+## Step-by-Step Implementation Order (RED → GREEN → REFACTOR)
+
+Dependency order: types → `coordKey` → `winCheck` → `move` → `history` → reducer. Each
+step: write the test(s) RED, implement to GREEN, REFACTOR. Run `npm test` after each GREEN.
+
+**Wave 0 — types (no tests; compile-only).**
+1. Append `Level`, `GameState`, `HistoryEntry`, `AnimSpec` to `src/types.ts` (per
+   signatures above). Run `npx tsc --noEmit` → GREEN (compiles). No RED step here — types
+   have no runtime behavior; the RED gate is the first test that imports them.
+
+**Wave 1 — `coordKey` + `winCheck` (tests #7–#10).**
+2. RED: write `tests/unit/core/winCheck.test.ts` with tests #7–#10. The file imports
+   `winCheck` from `src/core/winCheck.ts` which does not exist yet → RED (import error).
+3. GREEN: create `src/core/coordKey.ts` and `src/core/winCheck.ts` per signatures. Tests
+   #7–#10 pass.
+4. REFACTOR: none expected (the `coordKey` rebuild is already the minimal form).
+
+**Wave 2 — `move` (tests #1–#6).**
+5. RED: write `tests/unit/core/move.test.ts` with tests #1–#6. Import errors → RED.
+6. GREEN: implement `src/core/move.ts` per signature. Tests #1–#6 pass.
+7. REFACTOR: decide whether `move` returns the same `boxes` ref on a walk (recommended) or
+   always copies. Keep the same-ref optimization only if tests still read cleanly;
+   otherwise simplify to always-copy.
+
+**Wave 3 — `history` (tests #11–#14).**
+8. RED: write `tests/unit/core/history.test.ts` with tests #11–#14. RED.
+9. GREEN: implement `src/core/history.ts` per signature. Tests #11–#14 pass.
+10. REFACTOR: none expected.
+
+**Wave 4 — `reducer` + `createInitialState` (tests #15–#25).**
+11. RED: write `tests/unit/core/reducer.test.ts` with tests #15–#25. RED.
+12. GREEN: implement `src/core/reducer.ts` (including `createInitialState` and
+    `MOVE_DURATION_MS`) per signature. Tests #15–#25 pass.
+13. REFACTOR: remove the `as GameState` cast in `createInitialState` by constructing the
+    full state with `won: false` first, then `state.won = winCheck(state)` before returning
+    (cleaner; avoids the cast). Re-run tests → still GREEN.
+
+**Wave 5 — full-suite gate.**
+14. Run `npm test` → all `tests/unit/**/*.test.ts` (ph.1 smoke + ph.2 core) GREEN, exit 0.
+15. Run `npx tsc --noEmit` → GREEN (no type errors, `noUncheckedIndexedAccess` +
+    `verbatimModuleSyntax` satisfied across all new files).
+16. Run `npm run build` → GREEN (confirms no DOM import leaked into `src/core/` — a DOM
+    import would break the node-env `unit` project and/or the build).
+
+**Defer to ph.3 / ph.5 / ph.8** (non-goals per context.md):
+- `boxesOnTargets(state)` helper → ph.3 (renderer needs it).
+- Animator consuming `AnimSpec` → ph.5.
+- Deadlock (corner-trap) detection → ph.8.
+- Level loader / validator → ph.3.
